  <description><![CDATA[<p>Owned by the fourth generation of the Brettermeier family, the Gardenhotel Theresia is named after the siblings' great grandmother who founded the family business in 1948.</p>
<h2>Ski-in, Ski-out</h2>
<p>The hotel has ski-in, ski-out access using the T-bar across the road which connects to the main <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/austria/skicircus-saalbach-hinterglemm-leogang-fieberbrunn" target="_blank">Ski Circus</a> area. The ski bus stops outside and each room has its own heated and lockable cabinet to keep your ski gear.</p>
<p>You are located between Saalbach and Hinterglemm meaning you are short distance from either. The great bus and lift links make it easy to get around.</p>
<h2>Eco Hotel</h2>
<p>Gardenhotel Theresia is proud to have been the first certified organic hotel in Salzburg Land. They offer high quality organic cuisine from the alpine region.</p>
<p>The hotel is heated with green energy and has a strong focus on eco-philosophy to preserve the environment around it. </p>
<h2>Wellness</h2>
<p>The hotel's Mountain Green Spa uses mountain spring water in all their pools. The wellness area includes an outdoor adventure pool, outdoor Jacuzzi within the snowy gardens, indoor pool complex, and fitness centre. There is also a spa area including a cold bath, whirlpool, sauna, solarium and cooling area.</p>
<h2>Family Friendly</h2>
<p>The hotel features a kid's club with supervision, play area, and extensive kids programme for children aged 3 and up, giving adults the chance to unwind in the spa. There is a teenager’s lounge with indoor table tennis, pool table, table football, ping pong table, Nintendo switch and air hockey providing entertainment for older children. The kids' practice ski area and lift is conveniently located opposite the hotel for easy access.</p>
<h2>Family-run</h2>
<p>You can expect high standards of family-run service at the Gardenhotel Theresia, enriched by the personal touches of each family member. The hotel's ambiance is enhanced by a collection of paintings, carefully chosen by the father, adding a touch of artistic elegance. The mother, a former ski champion, shares her invaluable insider tips about the slopes, ensuring guests have the best skiing experience. Adding to this family heritage, the three siblings, Anna, Harald, and Franz-Josef, have been actively involved in the business since the fourth generation. They bring a combination of fresh, modern ideas and authenticity to the family enterprise, seamlessly blending tradition with innovation to enhance the guest experience at this family-run hotel.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Gardenhotel Theresia making us the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
